OL,3,C'I cried my eyes out': Pregnant women
OL,4,Cunable to give birth at home
OL,6,FITV Channel reporter Verity Wishart
OL,7,Fspoke to Amanda Berresford about her
OL,8,Fwishes to give birth at home.
OL,10,FPregnant women in Jersey are currently
OL,11,Funable to give birth at home while a
OL,12,Freview into safety is carried out.
OL,14,FThe home birth service supported 34
OL,15,Fhome births in 2023 and nine home
OL,16,Fbirths in 2024, however, the service
OL,17,Fwas temporarily paused on 14 October
OL,18,F2024.
