OL,3,C'I cried my eyes out': Pregnant women
OL,4,Cunable to give birth at home
OL,6,FJersey's Maternity Unit says they are
OL,7,Fworking to resume the service as soon
OL,8,Fas possible, after carrying out the
OL,9,Fnecessary training for midwives and
OL,10,Flooking into staff numbers.
OL,12,FThey added home births haven't always
OL,13,Fbeen possible due to ongoing staffing
OL,14,Fissues.
OL,16,FOne expectant mother, Amanda
OL,17,FBerresford said: "I have always dreamt
OL,18,Fof having a home birth, it aligns with
OL,19,Fmy philosophy, my cultural and
OL,20,Freligious beliefs.
