OL,6,F"I cried my eyes out.
OL,8,F"I am a taxpayer and I think this
OL,9,Fshould be offered to me.
OL,11,F"If they do not support me, I am going
OL,12,Fto do something called a free birth,
OL,13,Fwhich is riskier. I will birth here
OL,14,Fwith my husband."
