OL,6,F"Although the home birth service is
OL,7,Ftemporarily paused, while we conduct
OL,8,Fan internal review, we remain fully
OL,9,Fcommitted to reinstating it promptly
OL,10,Fonce the review is completed and we
OL,11,Fhave implemented any enhancements
OL,12,Fneeded to further improve the service."
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV News she said: " I
OL,15,Fneed to make sure that I am supporting
OL,16,Fmy colleagues, all the midwives, and
OL,17,Fmaking sure they get the appropriate
OL,18,Ftraining.
