OL,3,C'I cried my eyes out': Pregnant women
OL,4,Cunable to give birth at home
OL,6,F"Home birth is great when you've got
OL,7,Ftraining, and equipment and you can
OL,8,Fprovide it twenty-four-seven. I
OL,9,Fabsolutely get they don't think they
OL,10,Fhave a choice, but we have excellent
OL,11,Ffacilities within the hospital."
OL,13,FHowever, in Guernsey the option of a
OL,14,Fhome birth was scrapped in 2022 to cut
OL,15,Fcosts, leaving women without the
OL,16,Foption altogether.
OL,18,FAntenatal educator, Anita Davis in
OL,19,FGuernsey says it's a "woman's right"
OL,20,Fto have a home birth.
