OL,3,C'I cried my eyes out': Pregnant women
OL,4,Cunable to give birth at home
OL,6,F"They've been funnelled into the only
OL,7,Fprovision which is available which is
OL,8,Fa competent, working hospital but it's
OL,9,Fnot what they want."
OL,11,FIt is standard practice to carry out
OL,12,Freviews across medical services to
OL,13,Fmonitor performance and see whether
OL,14,Fimprovements can be made. The review
OL,15,Fincludes an assessment of protocols,
OL,16,Ftraining, and resources.
